title: 238.27 INTERFERENCE WITH FACILITIES.
text: No person may interfere with the installation, operation, inspection, maintenance, or removal of cable communications facilities or activities of a cable communications system under sections 238.02, subdivisions 1a, 1c, 1d, 21a, 28a, 29a, 31a, and 31d, and 238.22 to 238.27.
